  1Hz (0.1s on, 0.9s off) while a 3D GPS fix is acquired
  2Hz (0.1s on, 0.4s off) while the Iridium time is acquired
  
 If the LED stays on continuously, the test has passed
 If the LED goes off, the test has failed

